WEBVTT

00:02:58.195 --> 00:03:01.005
Galaksi zitaanza kukimbizana kukaribiana,

00:03:01.005 --> 00:03:02.495
na zikijikusanya pamoja

00:03:02.495 --> 00:03:06.015
nguvu zao za uvutano zingekua
na nguvu zaidi.

00:03:06.015 --> 00:03:09.205
Nyota pia zingekusanyika pamoja
na kugongana.

00:03:09.205 --> 00:03:13.205
Joto lingepanda kadri anga
inavyozidi kujibana zaidi.

00:03:13.205 --> 00:03:15.485
Ukubwa waa ulimwengu ungekua timazi

00:03:15.485 --> 00:03:19.165
hadi kila kitu kilichojikusanyika
kwenye nafasi ndogo

00:03:19.165 --> 00:03:24.165
mpaka hadi chembe za atomu na atomu
ndogo vitajikusanyika pamoja.

00:03:24.165 --> 00:03:29.666
Matokeo yatakuwa ni ulimwengu mzito,
wenye joto na ulio jifunga ---

00:03:29.666 --> 00:03:32.346
kama ile hali iliyoitangulia Big Bang.